{"tid":2347828,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大女生向路軌擲竹枝囚8個月求減刑 高院法官押後裁決","createTime":"2020-12-31T10:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T12:05:27.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"62427c2439971f00e7211aefcf337cf686c68bda","tid":2347828,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:18:57.000Z","msg":"網民去年11月發起「黎明行動」，堵塞交通兼發起三罷。就讀中大心理系的女生早前在裁判法院承認向東鐵線大埔段路軌投擲竹枝及拒捕，被判囚8個月。女生今就刑期向高等法院提出上訴，指本案案情不如外國案例般嚴重。至於原審主任裁判官蘇文隆批評女生沒有勸阻同案12歲男童離開現場是「罪加一等」，上訴人指犯案者當時蒙面，「點會諗到咁多嘢」。法官李運騰聽取控辯雙方陳詞後，押後宣判。<br />\n<br />\n李官聽取陳詞後表示，控辯雙方呈上了大量案例，需時閱讀及考慮裁決，所以押後宣判，希望一個月內頒佈判決。李官亦批准被告繼續保釋等候判決，惟明言批准保釋不代表就上訴的勝算有任何暗示。"},{"pid":"a72eacf3e5f25b17df36052153874067e06c1c14","tid":2347828,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/PW67VZPGVVBAJBCLVIBLRR523Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FPW67VZPGVVBAJBCLVIBLRR523Q%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=61f111b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FPW67VZPGVVBAJBCLVIBLRR523Q%2F&h=6436f1d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/PW67VZPGVVBAJBCLVIBLRR523Q/</a>"},{"pid":"0fb1409c86b72a72846bc257df45ebcc19f38407","tid":2347828,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1743f0ef4562efcabd0f65303bfa81df820f66e0","tid":2347828,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"原審主任裁判官蘇文隆判刑指，上訴人未有勸阻有份犯案的12歲男童，或是將他趕回家，反而忍心夥同他犯案，<strong><span class=\"red\">實屬「沒有道義，缺乏人性，罪加一等」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cl